<section class="brand--department-for-business-innovation-skills brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What Groceries Code Adjudicator does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>The Groceries Code Adjudicator (the GCA) is the independent regulator ensuring that regulated retailers treat their direct suppliers lawfully and fairly.</p>

<p><abbr title="Groceries Code Adjudicator">GCA</abbr> works with the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy">Department for Business, Energy & Industrial Strategy</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/groceries-code-adjudicator/about" class="brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>



